name: Fired on Mars
overview: After taking a one-way trip to the Red Planet, graphic designer Jeff Cooper finds himself adrift when his bosses unceremoniously eliminate his role.

episodes.name: The One Way Trip
episodes.overview: Millions of miles from his earthbound girlfriend Hannah, graphic designer Jeff finds himself jobless on Mars after his position is unceremoniously eliminated.

episodes.name: The Book of Reagan
episodes.overview: A worse-for-wear Jeff lands an internship with the Dreamspiration team and falls under the spell of fanatical executive assistant Jaxton Olivier.

episodes.name: 12 Rules for Extraordinary People
episodes.overview: In the aftermath of Reagan’s explosive birthday party, Jeff finds himself at a crossroads, while Jaxton faces the sleep tank.

episodes.name: Banana Express
episodes.overview: After Martin offers him a job performing back-breaking manual labor, Jeff’s life begins to turn around ... until he stumbles upon a dangerous secret.

episodes.name: The God of War
episodes.overview: Invigorated by his newfound community of rebels, Jeff faces a dilemma when Brandon offers him a new opportunity at Mars.ly.

episodes.name: Back in the High Life Again
episodes.overview: Jeff finds himself in over his head as he secretly works for Mars.ly's anniversary campaign while prepping The Buckies' for their imminent departure.

episodes.name: The Fibonacci Sequence
episodes.overview: The Buckies scramble to avoid being caught while Jeff slips further to the dark side of Mar.sly corporate.
